ss=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104aea1665702753575.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aea1665702753575.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aea1665702753575.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"aea1665702753575\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /rpcencoded\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Create an RPC/Encoded WSDL file from the signature of a Uniface signature.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aea1665702753575__section_w2610ab1b5b1_w2611ab1b5_w2612ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aea1665702753575__p_d150860e1_d150861e1_d150862e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">/rpcencoded</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aea1665702753575__section_w2613ab1b5b3_w2614ab1b5_w2615ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d243887e60\">\n                  \n Used With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aea1665702753575__p_d150866e1_d150867e1_d150868e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"grk1665702753295.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/grk1665702753295.html\" title=\"Export interface definitions to integrate call-in from various types of middleware, or generate Java files for Java call-in, or generate C call-out stub code.\">/sto</a>\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rdi1665702753224.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rdi1665702753224.html\" title=\"Specify the type of middleware used for call-out or call-in when importing or exporting of interface definitions.\">/mwr</a> =ws</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"aea1665702753575__section_w2616ab1b5b5_w2617ab1b5_w2618ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d243887e83\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aea1665702753575__p_d150872e1_d150873e1_d150874e1\">With the <code class=\"ph codeph\">/rpcencoded</code> subswitch,\n            the binding style of the exported WSDL file is RPC/Encoded. Without the\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">/rpcencoded</code> subswitch, the binding style is Document/Literal\n            Wrapped.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ukw1665702547648.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>WSDL</a><p>The Web Services Description Language (WSDL) is an XML-based language for describing Web services and how to access them.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ter1665702547737.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Exporting WSDL and Schema Files for Web Services Call-In</a><p>The WSDL export facility creates WSDL and XSD files from Uniface signatures. These files are used by web service requesters to call the web service.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525643\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525643\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/rpcencoded Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /rpcencoded Create an RPC/Encoded WSDL file from the signature of a Uniface signature. /rpcencoded Used With /sto /mwr =ws Description With the /rpcencoded subswitch, the binding style of the exported WSDL file is RPC/Encoded. Without the /rpcencoded subswitch, the binding style is Document/Literal Wrapped. Related Links WSDL The Web Services Description Language (WSDL) is an XML-based language for describing Web services and how to access them. Exporting WSDL and Schema Files for Web Services Call-In The WSDL export facility creates WSDL and XSD files from Uniface signatures. These files are used by web service requesters to call the web service. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}